{"title":"Protect, power and personalise your iPhone 16 with these MagSafe accessories.","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/2451100/protect-power-and-personalise-your-iphone-16-with-these-magsafe-accessories.html","date":1725915600000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.macworld.com\">Macworld</a></p>\n\n<div>\n<section><div></div></section>\n\n\n\n<p>The new iPhone 16 devices have arrived, promising to be some of the most in-demand tech products over the next year. Thanks to the MagSafe wireless charging used by Apple, there’s also a whole world of accessories to help you get the most out of these new handsets.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Spigen has been at the forefront of protective smartphone cases for the last 16 years, and its <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?maas=maas_adg_D4FC0A6A6AFED14C3ADE33D867E49CA1_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas&amp;isPreview=1&amp;isSlp=1&amp;asins=B0D7B2CXXN,B0D7BJLPQK,B0D21RLDPY,B0D21WZ8RN,B0CMRXQBM8,B0D2PMWC5F,B0CMS23Z5S,B0C4G46MZ1,B0CF5249VG,B0D13XY2GW,B0CP338FH2,B0CP328MN3,B0BLT5QWW7,B0BT291727\" target=\"_blank\">MagFit ecosystem</a> has everything you need to protect, power and accessorize that shiny, new Apple device.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>A MagSafe case is where it starts</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A great case is an essential purchase for any iPhone when it comes to protecting and stylising your device. But, it’s also important that MagSafe charging works seamlessly. Spigen has plenty of options that cover these bases.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>The <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?maas=maas_adg_823D0C7FE4F99DDFBA28FB1A1499C140_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas&amp;isPreview=1&amp;isSlp=1&amp;asins=B0D222B155,B0D7B2CXXN,B0D221LFPN,B0D7BJLPQK,B0CBD34N2V,B0CBD145GW\" target=\"_blank\">Enzo Aramid</a> ($39.99), with its sleek matte black livery and Aerocore Aramid materials, delivers professional looks and solid protection. While the futuristic, multi-layered design of the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?maas=maas_adg_D96F0A8C46D8F60863DB1DE0D96EAB5B_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas&amp;isPreview=1&amp;isSlp=1&amp;asins=B0D21RLDPY,B0D21WQD4C,B0D21WZ8RN,B0D21XY884,B0CB775ZNS,B0C5S9JVJR,B0CB78D95C,B0C5S8XT5F,B0CB77TMHP,B0C5S823XJ,B0CB78GW7K,B0C5S961WX\" target=\"_blank\">Ultra Hybrid Zero: One</a> ($22.99) looks like you can see right into the heart of your new iPhone.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Safely carry your cards with a MagSafe wallet</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_02.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>A <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?maas=maas_adg_25EDED3CF152635C5C05A56427D54BFE_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas&amp;isPreview=1&amp;isSlp=1&amp;asins=B0CMRXQBM8,B0D2PMWC5F,B0CMS23Z5S,B0C4G46MZ1,B0CG11C3HX,B0CN1SMRWM,B0CMRW7JTJ,B0CYHMNDPF,B0CYJ3VYKB,B0CYHP2CFX\" target=\"_blank\">MagSafe wallet</a> attaches to the back of your iPhone, saving space while adding the convenience of having everything easily to hand. Spigen’s MagFit system has several options, all with anti-slip patterning that ensures the wallet stays snugly in place.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They come with quick-access slots that allow you to slide out your cards smoothly. So, no struggling to prise your credit card free while everyone in the cashier’s line waits impatiently behind.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Wirelessly charge your iPhone 16 with MagFit at home or on the go</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_03.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>If you want to turn your iPhone into a bedside clock while it’s charging, then the Standby Mode in iOS works brilliantly with the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Spigen-ArcField-Magnetic-Wireless-Charging/dp/B0CF5249VG?maas=maas_adg_C6069CAE32143B08FD642DA74F5B314C_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas\" target=\"_blank\">ArcField Duo</a> ($49.49) to achieve this, while simultaneously charging your AirPods. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Recharging your iPhone in the car is also important, as Apple Maps can quickly drain the battery or the sun cause the iPhone to overheat. Both of these problems can be solved by using the Spigen <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?maas=maas_adg_87438BD0147D0C7E1C0CB17879CBD08C_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas&amp;isPreview=1&amp;isSlp=1&amp;asins=B0CP338FH2,B0CP328MN3\" target=\"_blank\">OneTap Pro 3 CryoMax</a> ($52.99). As the compact, adjustable MagSafe charger brings the added bonus of cooling your iPhone while charging.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Other cool MagSafe accessories to make life easier</h2>\n\n\n<div><figure><img src=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all&amp;w=1200\" alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" />\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div><div><figure><img alt=\"Spigen SponCon MagFit\" srcset=\"https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?quality=50&amp;strip=all 1600w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=300%2C168&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 300w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=768%2C432&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 768w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1200%2C675&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1200w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1536%2C864&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1536w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=1240%2C697&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 1240w, https://b2c-contenthub.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/pr_macworld_iphone16_04.jpg?resize=150%2C84&amp;quality=50&amp;strip=all 150w\" width=\"1200\" height=\"675\" loading=\"lazy\" /></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div></div>\n\t\t</div></figure><p>Spigen</p></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Spigen’s MagFit ecosystem comes with plenty of other helpful accessories that use the MagSafe design. For instance, the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Spigen-Magsafe-MacBook-Magnetic-Designed/dp/B0BLT5QWW7?maas=maas_adg_F394B13F9108FBE7F47999478FA3DF87_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas\" target=\"_blank\">OM101</a> ($21.99) is a clever magnetic grip with an adjustable ring that can help you hold your iPhone, act as a kickstand for watching video content, plus there’s also a clip that enables you to attach it to the top of a laptop for FaceTime calls.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you’re travelling, then the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Spigen-OneTap-Flight-Designed-MagSafe/dp/B0BT291727?maas=maas_adg_9D4006D143B8A0B779161A10255AC235_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas&amp;th=1&amp;psc=1\" target=\"_blank\">OneTap Away</a> ($39.99) could be a godsend. Designed to clip onto an upright tray table on a plane, this instantly turns your iPhone into your in-flight entertainment system. You can angle the stand to adjust to your preferred eyeline, then watch TV shows or movies, all while keeping your hands free.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Get the most out of your iPhone with the Spigen MagFit system</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>As you can see, there’s plenty of fantastic accessories in the MagFit system that are purpose-built to make light work of protecting, styling, charging and using your iPhone 16 or any other MagSafe equipped iPhone. If you’re buying a new Apple device, then a trip to the <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/213E57C8-E995-40D3-96F9-A551C0788461?maas=maas_adg_DDC094F4CF9D9F490103D5F427915FA9_afap_abs&amp;ref_=aa_maas&amp;tag=maas\" target=\"_blank\">Spigen MagFit page</a> could be the perfect upgrade.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><div>\n\n</div></figure>\n\n</div>","author":"","siteTitle":"Macworld","siteHash":"37e84dd5a21fa961d6d6630e269546024dbb7741b2e2fadbe74f47383c70dfbb","entryHash":"3ac424eedd4db9c6fcf6ec4ce02773883a154574c5e06c07ae3fd89e257c3938","category":"Apple"}